  "system": {
    "description": "<p>This weapon is a shrunken down version of a chainsaw exchanging the large, loud gasoline engine and big hooked teeth for a small electric motor with a microwire blade. Microwire chainsaws can not accept any upgrade on their contact. This blade may also be used as a bayonet on any weapon with a bayonet lug. Microwire chainsaws require the Exotic Melee Weapons Proficiency feat in order to be used without a &minus;4 attack penalty, even when used as a bayonet.</p>",
